window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Casting necromancy without ever learning how to isn't supposed to be possible. </b></p> <p>A starving orphan girl named Vita is somehow managing it anyway, and she's not sure if this is going to be the solution to her life's problems or a horrifying, spiraling mess of problems she can hardly conceive.</p> <p>Set in a massive world of floating islands with a dangerous entity known as the Mistwatcher that lurks beneath them, <i>Vigor Mortis</i> pairs adorable charm with haunting fantasy.</p>"; 
